name: Thurston County Public Health Medical Reserve Corp

info: This is a single-dose Johnson & Johnson clinic being held at Capital Mall, 625 Black Lake Blvd SW, Olympia WA, 98502 for anyone age 18 and older from 12pm until mall closing.  We will be located inside the mall, closest to the Sephora end of the mall and next to the Buckle store. info:
This is a clinic for 1st or 2nd doses of the Pfizer COVID-19 vaccine or the single dose of the Johnson & Johnson*** All patients 12 years old and older can register for the Pfizer vaccine only. (If 12-17 years old for the Pfizer vaccine, you must be with a parent or guardian or have parental/guardian consent)

 ***Residents of ANY state are now eligible for the vaccine, but you still must have photo ID***

info:
This is a Pfizer vaccination event for anyone age 12 and older.
